-Users can create an account
-Users can login to their account
-Users can see all recipes
-Users can see all cooking tips
-Users can search through recipes and cooking tips
-Recipes will have a title
-Recipes will have a picture
-Recipes will have directions
-Recipes will have reviews
-Users can create recipes
-Users can create shopping listsj
-Shopping Lists will have a title relative to the recipe
-Shopping lists will list all ingredients and quantities
